      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# Compact PropertyGrid Design Test\n\nThis notebook showcases the new compact PropertyGrid design with table layout.\n\n## Design Improvements ✨\n- 📏 **Compact layout** - reduced vertical padding and spacing\n- 📊 **Table structure** - proper column widths, minimal property column\n- 🎨 **Theme colors** - backgrounds from theme variables\n- ✏️ **Subtle pencil icon** - replaces the \"Editable\" badge\n- 🖱️ **Hover effects** - pencil appears on value hover"
    },
    {
      "id": "code_compact",
      "type": "code",
      "code": "// Compact configuration object to test table layout\nexports.settings = {\n  app: \"CoolApp\",\n  ver: \"3.1.4\",\n  debug: true,\n  port: 8080,\n  ssl: false,\n  timeout: 30000,\n  retries: 3,\n  cache: true,\n  \n  db: {\n    host: \"prod-db\",\n    port: 5432,\n    name: \"app_prod\",\n    pool: 20,\n    ssl: true\n  },\n  \n  api: {\n    v1: \"/api/v1\",\n    v2: \"/api/v2\",\n    health: \"/ping\",\n    metrics: \"/stats\"\n  },\n  \n  features: {\n    auth: true,\n    logs: true,\n    metrics: false,\n    cache: true,\n    beta: {\n      ui: false,\n      api: true,\n      perf: false\n    }\n  }\n};\n\noutput(exports.settings);"
    },
    {
      "id": "md_test",
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "## Design Features to Notice\n\n1. **Compact Table Layout**:\n   - Property names in narrow left column\n   - Values take remaining space\n   - Minimal vertical padding\n   - Clean borders and spacing\n\n2. **Theme Integration**:\n   - Property column uses `bg-muted/30`\n   - Value column uses `bg-background`\n   - Headers use theme colors\n   - Consistent with app theme\n\n3. **Subtle Editable Indicator**:\n   - Small pencil icon in header (instead of badge)\n   - Hover pencil icons on editable values\n   - No visual clutter\n\n4. **Hierarchical Display**:\n   - Click chevrons to expand/collapse\n   - Nested indentation\n   - Clean nesting visualization\n\n**Try editing some values** and notice the compact, clean interface!"
    },
